                <Paragraph>
                    <Run FontFamily="Palatino Linotype" Text="The investment of this portfolio was created in order to track its performance during the periods between 09/12/2004 to 12/03/2004 against the performance of the market, represented by the Dow Jones Industrial Average (DJIA). The performance of the portfolio was monitored on  a weekly basis.  "/>
                    <Run Text="The investment portfolio is composed by seven companies traded at New York Stock Exchange. Exactly two of them are part of the Dow Jones Industrial Average Index.  My investment constraint was $5,000. On Sunday, September 9"/>
                    <Span Typography.Variants="Superscript">
                        <Run Text="th"/>
                    </Span>
                    <Run Text=", I bought stocks at NYSE at a closing price. The analysis of this portfolio includes any reason for any deviations between the portfolio and the DJIA Index. Possible reasons included the 2004 Election, industry markets, and particular companies' financial aims.  Based on probabilities a projection of the portfolio is also made for next one year with reasons. To create balanced portfolio, companies from industrial sectors were included. Diverse areas like Money Center Banks, Technology, Retail, Chemicals, and Manufactures were considered. In the following lines a brief explanation about each selected company is given."/>
