                <Paragraph FontFamily="Palatino Linotype" Margin="0" TextAlignment="Justify">
                    <Run Text="Textron Inc. is a multi-industry company with operations in five business segments. The Bell segment manufactures military helicopters and tiltrotor aircraft for the United States Government and commercial helicopters for corporate, offshore, utility, charter, police, fire, rescue and emergency medical customers. It also supplies advanced weapon systems and piston aircraft engines to the defense and aerospace markets. The Cessna segment is primarily engaged in the manufacture of light- and mid-size business jets. Textron Fastening Systems is a provider of integrated fastening systems solutions. The Industrial segment designs, manufactures and sells golf carts and turf-care equipment, plastic fuel systems, wire and cable installation equipment, and industrial pumps and gears. Textron Financial Corporation is a diversified commercial finance business with core operations in aircraft finance, asset-based lending, distribution finance, golf finance, resort finance and structured capital."/>
